  <!--
    UWP variant of the CompositionExpressions library. Compiles the same
    source files that ..\CompositionExpressions.WinAppSdk consumes (the
    typed expression-AST + animatable-node wrappers + property-set helper
    + animation-property-name registry) but against the UAP target so
    classic UWP apps can take a NuGet dependency on the typed-expressions
    DSL without pulling in the WinAppSdk hosting story.

    Sources physically live under ..\CompositionCollectionView\ to keep a
    single canonical copy; both this project and the WinAppSdk twin
    Compile Include them. CompositionCollectionView.csproj
    ProjectReferences this assembly and excludes the same paths from its
    own compile set.

    Note: TrackedInteractionNodes.cs is intentionally excluded — it uses
    Microsoft.UI.Composition.Interactions APIs that don't have a UWP
    counterpart we want to ship today. The WinAppSdk twin includes it.
  -->
